  "detailed_description": "Are you hungry? Do you want some yakiniku?<br><br>Let's play this game! Simple and easy!<br><br>Simulate to eating a yakiniku with no more calories!!!<br><br>Just chill out and simulate eating yakiniku!<br><br><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong><br><br>This game is so simple you can play with only 1 mode but can apply to several types of play.<br><br>1. Plain play<br>Nothing to do so much.. just play for fun or chat with friends.<br><br>2. Play with rice<br>If you hungry, you can enjoy your meal with only rice bowls. (You can add more sauce or salt for a good taste.)<br><br>3. Play with beer<br>Enjoy the yakiniku atmosphere with cold beer. It'll make you relax.<br><br>4. Play with salad.<br>Do you want to diet? Don't worry, this game will make your salad's taste better!!! Try it!!!<br><br>5. ETC<br>You can enjoy our game in a lot of ways. Please share with us for your play!<br><br><br><strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong><br><br>1. keep raw meat on the stove.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/e4aaa8a7e5b07eb569450f4476845704.poster.avif?t=1743093266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/e4aaa8a7e5b07eb569450f4476845704.webm?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/e4aaa8a7e5b07eb569450f4476845704.mp4?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2. Flip meat when you think it's OK.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/98673b8f4ece9d9e1f541bdedb7047de.poster.avif?t=1743093266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/98673b8f4ece9d9e1f541bdedb7047de.webm?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/98673b8f4ece9d9e1f541bdedb7047de.mp4?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>3. Beware it's OVERCOOK!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/c7e7333226a7feef6108a7245c6f5f85.poster.avif?t=1743093266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/c7e7333226a7feef6108a7245c6f5f85.webm?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/c7e7333226a7feef6108a7245c6f5f85.mp4?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>4. Throw away burned meat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/6008965245ff3ec8e2981711e6f54df6.poster.avif?t=1743093266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/6008965245ff3ec8e2981711e6f54df6.webm?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/6008965245ff3ec8e2981711e6f54df6.mp4?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>5. Keep perfect meat to sauce and eat it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/14e18f5ca2d27c6e2e76179e53507fdc.poster.avif?t=1743093266\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/14e18f5ca2d27c6e2e76179e53507fdc.webm?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001570/extras/14e18f5ca2d27c6e2e76179e53507fdc.mp4?t=1743093266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*This game is not support any controller BUT support with rice and beer!!!!<br><br>Enjoy your meal!!!!!!!",
